        "gg9MJALFpNT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/939c2057-a941-40a9-bf45-7f2ea682d1d2.webp",
        "ggA8BvoqhHx_text": "Small rituals.<br>Big difference",
        "ggI1nXJ9-LF_text": "In Italy, we have a concept called sprezzatura — the art of making the difficult look effortless. The elegance of a man who cares about how he looks without making a fuss about it.<br><br>This is the philosophy behind SerlinoLab. Products that deliver real results — less wrinkles, firmer skin, a fresher face — without complicated routines. Two minutes a day. That's all it takes",
        "ggSRP858VrP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ddce9c4e-19ad-40eb-a5dd-c16ca7a0476f.webp",
        "gganb4ETLPU_text": "Effortless results.<br>No fuss",
        "ggfGSrXvkGr_background_desktop_image_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/bg.png",
        "ggj1bU9OACR_text": "The Italian art of living — <strong>l'arte di vivere</strong> — is about appreciating small rituals. A good espresso. A sunset over the Mediterranean. A moment of care for yourself.<br>&nbsp;<br>SerlinoLab is that moment. Not a chore. Not a 10-step routine. <strong>A daily ritual that makes you look better and feel better</strong>",
        "ggl0NxBI-r8_text": "Crafted in Italy.<br>For the man who appreciates quality",
        "ggo_GLLes-J_background_desktop_image_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/bg.png",
        "ggoh5KeK7tb_text": "Since 1987, our family laboratory has been crafting skincare the Italian way — with patience, precision, and an obsession for quality over quantity",
        "ggp8gXoaj8e_text": "What we stand for",
        "ggptA4E7lnM_text": "<strong>Craftsmanship over marketing.</strong> We'd rather spend money on better ingredients than flashier ads.<br><br><strong>Timelessness over trends.</strong> We don't reformulate every season. We perfect one formula and stand by it.<br><br><strong>Results you can see.</strong> Not promises — proof. 60 days, or your money back",
        "ggxuZIrz0xi_text": "Crafted on the<br>Italian coast",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-612888062996775443"
